WEBVTT

STYLE
::cue {
font-size: 1em;
font-weight: bold;
color: #ffffff;
}

00:01:31.180 --> 00:01:34.700 line:80%
=Generation to Generation=

00:01:34.820 --> 00:01:37.700 line:80%
=Episode 18=

00:01:37.820 --> 00:01:40.180 line:80%
If the man in black
is truly the mastermind,

00:01:41.700 --> 00:01:43.570 line:80%
perhaps I might spare you.

00:01:44.090 --> 00:01:45.210 line:80%
He won't speak, but I'll.

00:01:47.650 --> 00:01:49.130 line:80%
The first time I saw the man in black

00:01:49.540 --> 00:01:51.290 line:80%
was not long after Nie Zhe
became the Chief.

00:01:51.490 --> 00:01:52.980 line:80%
Many in the sect refused to submit.

00:01:55.780 --> 00:01:57.010 line:80%
Kill those people,

00:01:57.570 --> 00:01:59.820 line:80%
and you can secure your position.

00:02:07.540 --> 00:02:09.396 line:80%
With the man in black's help,

00:02:09.407 --> 00:02:10.569 line:80%
Nie Zhe eliminated dissenters

00:02:10.580 --> 00:02:11.850 line:80%
and gradually secured his power.

00:02:12.140 --> 00:02:13.300 line:80%
From then on,

00:02:13.300 --> 00:02:15.300 line:80%
he obeyed the man
in black without question.

00:02:16.090 --> 00:02:18.810 line:80%
The man in black also gave him
Suzi Fragrance and Qianxun Wood.

00:02:19.690 --> 00:02:21.140 line:80%
Nie Zhe then forced me

00:02:21.580 --> 00:02:22.740 line:80%
to use the Suzi Fragrance

00:02:23.060 --> 00:02:24.490 line:80%
to poison your father.

00:02:24.930 --> 00:02:26.740 line:80%
Who exactly is the man in black?

00:02:27.180 --> 00:02:28.020 line:80%
That person

00:02:28.900 --> 00:02:30.530 line:80%
has never shown his true face.

00:02:31.020 --> 00:02:31.860 line:80%
Oh, right.

00:02:32.140 --> 00:02:35.060 line:80%
He also revealed Yin Dai's whereabouts.

00:02:35.060 --> 00:02:37.340 line:80%
That was how Nie Zhe had
the chance to kill Yin Dai

00:02:37.340 --> 00:02:39.090 line:80%
and avenge the former chief.

00:02:39.090 --> 00:02:40.930 line:80%
Even I can't find him.

00:02:40.930 --> 00:02:43.060 line:80%
You'll never be able to find him.

00:02:43.060 --> 00:02:45.690 line:80%
You'll never avenge your father.

00:02:45.970 --> 00:02:46.810 line:80%
Take him away.

00:02:52.530 --> 00:02:53.370 line:80%
Qingyan,

00:02:54.300 --> 00:02:56.300 line:80%
I have told you everything.

00:02:57.410 --> 00:02:59.020 line:80%
Can you spare me now?

00:03:02.860 --> 00:03:04.020 line:80%
I'll spare you.

00:03:06.620 --> 00:03:08.300 line:80%
I'll also leave you here

00:03:08.300 --> 00:03:09.180 line:80%
alone

00:03:10.740 --> 00:03:12.140 line:80%
to die of old age.

00:03:12.460 --> 00:03:13.200 line:80%
Qingyan.

00:03:13.300 --> 00:03:14.180 line:80%
Qingyan.

00:03:14.530 --> 00:03:15.580 line:80%
Qingyan!

00:03:15.810 --> 00:03:18.460 line:80%
I know I was wrong.

00:03:18.460 --> 00:03:20.210 line:80%
Please forgive me.

00:03:20.210 --> 00:03:21.490 line:80%
Qingyan!

00:03:25.300 --> 00:03:26.900 line:80%
Don't believe Nie Zhe.

00:03:28.410 --> 00:03:30.340 line:80%
The man in black supported him
for so many years.

00:03:30.780 --> 00:03:31.970 line:80%
He'll surely come to save him.

00:03:32.650 --> 00:03:34.020 line:80%
We'll wait here.

00:03:34.210 --> 00:03:35.370 line:80%
We'll definitely catch him.

00:04:05.180 --> 00:04:06.300 line:80%
He still hasn't come?

00:04:07.620 --> 00:04:09.900 line:80%
Has Nie Zhe become a discarded pawn?

00:04:09.900 --> 00:04:11.460 line:80%
He has schemed for so long.

00:04:12.210 --> 00:04:13.780 line:80%
He won't give up so easily.

00:04:13.780 --> 00:04:14.780 line:80%
I'm exhausted.

00:04:14.780 --> 00:04:15.620 line:80%
We'll wait slowly.

00:04:54.530 --> 00:04:55.410 line:80%
Young Master...

00:05:00.820 --> 00:05:01.660 line:80%
What is it?

00:05:01.996 --> 00:05:03.650 line:80%
The Jade Sunflower
isn't in the treasury.

00:05:03.650 --> 00:05:04.490 line:80%
It has been stolen.

00:05:11.850 --> 00:05:12.690 line:80%
Lu Chengnan?

00:05:14.940 --> 00:05:17.340 line:80%
Isn't he Nie Hengcheng's most trusted

00:05:17.340 --> 00:05:19.090 line:80%
and most valued disciple?

00:05:19.900 --> 00:05:21.580 line:80%
Why would he steal the Jade Sunflower?

00:05:21.580 --> 00:05:23.290 line:80%
No idea.

00:05:23.290 --> 00:05:25.140 line:80%
After Nie Hengcheng discovered it,

00:05:25.140 --> 00:05:26.530 line:80%
he was furious

00:05:26.530 --> 00:05:28.140 line:80%
and injured Lu Chengnan.

00:05:28.140 --> 00:05:29.970 line:80%
I was there at the time.

00:05:29.970 --> 00:05:32.410 line:80%
Nie Hengcheng was like a madman,

00:05:32.410 --> 00:05:33.780 line:80%
striking without restraint.

00:05:33.780 --> 00:05:35.530 line:80%
He meant to kill him.

00:05:35.530 --> 00:05:38.820 line:80%
When Han Yisu saw
Nie Hengcheng's intent to kill,

00:05:38.820 --> 00:05:41.780 line:80%
he desperately tried to stop him

00:05:41.780 --> 00:05:44.580 line:80%
while shouting for Lu Chengnan to run.

00:05:45.380 --> 00:05:46.340 line:80%
I haven't seen

00:05:46.340 --> 00:05:48.210 line:80%
Lu Chengnan since.

00:05:49.170 --> 00:05:52.020 line:80%
The Jade Sunflower is also missing.

00:05:52.020 --> 00:05:53.580 line:80%
This Jade Sunflower

00:05:53.580 --> 00:05:55.610 line:80%
is merely a healing item

00:05:55.610 --> 00:05:57.730 line:80%
to calm the mind and warm the meridians.

00:05:57.730 --> 00:05:59.650 line:80%
Why would Nie Hengcheng value it so much

00:06:00.340 --> 00:06:02.780 line:80%
that he'd injure his trusted disciple?

00:06:02.780 --> 00:06:05.780 line:80%
Lu Chengnan was even the next chief.

00:06:06.210 --> 00:06:09.700 line:80%
Why offend Nie Hengcheng
over a mere object?

00:06:10.940 --> 00:06:11.940 line:80%
Young Master,

00:06:11.940 --> 00:06:14.140 line:80%
our treasury holds so many treasures.

00:06:14.530 --> 00:06:16.410 line:80%
Why did you ask specifically

00:06:16.410 --> 00:06:18.140 line:80%
about the Jade Sunflower?

00:06:20.460 --> 00:06:21.300 line:80%
To repay a favor.

00:06:24.500 --> 00:06:27.020 line:80%
The Wanzai Stone beneath Mount Lieyan?

00:06:28.500 --> 00:06:30.500 line:80%
Though it can't eradicate
the Nether Aura,

00:06:31.170 --> 00:06:33.020 line:80%
its effect of warming the meridians

00:06:33.020 --> 00:06:34.170 line:80%
is exceptional.

00:06:34.970 --> 00:06:36.970 line:80%
I hope you won't disdain it

00:06:36.970 --> 00:06:38.050 line:80%
and accept it.

00:06:40.977 --> 00:06:43.050 line:80%
The chaos caused by Nie Zhe
has yet to be resolved.

00:06:43.210 --> 00:06:44.530 line:80%
The Jade Sunflower

00:06:44.530 --> 00:06:46.610 line:80%
may have fallen elsewhere.

00:06:46.610 --> 00:06:48.460 line:80%
If I find it one day,

00:06:48.460 --> 00:06:50.340 line:80%
I'll immediately deliver it to you.

00:06:50.970 --> 00:06:51.810 line:80%
Thanks.

00:06:55.140 --> 00:06:56.610 line:80%
Since you've found this,

00:06:57.460 --> 00:06:59.460 line:80%
you should return early to recuperate.

00:06:59.970 --> 00:07:00.810 line:80%
How about this?

00:07:01.380 --> 00:07:02.500 line:80%
Tomorrow morning,

00:07:02.500 --> 00:07:04.460 line:80%
I'll send someone to escort you out.

00:07:07.500 --> 00:07:08.820 line:80%
Will Zhao leave with me?

00:07:11.650 --> 00:07:12.836 line:80%
She has matters to attend to,

00:07:13.530 --> 00:07:15.340 line:80%
so she won't leave with you.

00:07:15.820 --> 00:07:17.140 line:80%
Do you still remember

00:07:18.020 --> 00:07:20.140 line:80%
what we said about following
the natural course?

00:07:20.580 --> 00:07:22.020 line:80%
During this trip,

00:07:22.020 --> 00:07:24.340 line:80%
I witnessed Nie Zhe's cruelty.

00:07:24.340 --> 00:07:26.730 line:80%
I now know the rumors
about Li Sect are not false.

00:07:27.380 --> 00:07:28.700 line:80%
Our feud runs deep.

00:07:29.140 --> 00:07:31.140 line:80%
Centuries of blood debts and division

00:07:31.140 --> 00:07:33.020 line:80%
can't be resolved in a single day.

00:07:34.380 --> 00:07:35.610 line:80%
Speak plainly.

00:07:37.460 --> 00:07:39.020 line:80%
Zhao won't stay.

00:07:39.530 --> 00:07:41.020 line:80%
The overall situation here is settled.

00:07:41.020 --> 00:07:42.020 line:80%
In a few days,

00:07:42.610 --> 00:07:44.210 line:80%
we'll return.

00:07:57.140 --> 00:07:59.650 line:80%
This mountain map is so detailed.

00:08:00.020 --> 00:08:01.460 line:80%
Since you wanted to see it,

00:08:01.460 --> 00:08:03.500 line:80%
I asked them for the most complete copy.

00:08:05.580 --> 00:08:07.020 line:80%
Miss Cai,

00:08:07.020 --> 00:08:08.900 line:80%
are we still waiting here tonight?

00:08:09.940 --> 00:08:10.970 line:80%
Of course.

00:08:11.380 --> 00:08:12.900 line:80%
If we don't catch the culprit,

00:08:12.900 --> 00:08:15.090 line:80%
how can we console Uncle Chang's spirit?

00:08:15.380 --> 00:08:17.020 line:80%
If that person never comes,

00:08:17.340 --> 00:08:19.210 line:80%
will you keep waiting?

00:08:25.913 --> 00:08:27.752 line:80%
(Starry Terrace, Sandy Ridge)
How vast.

00:08:27.763 --> 00:08:30.448 line:80%
No wonder the mountains have sustained
Li Sect for over 200 years.

00:08:30.459 --> 00:08:31.650 line:80%
Naturally.

00:08:31.650 --> 00:08:33.330 line:80%
Our mountains have always been rich

00:08:33.330 --> 00:08:34.683 line:80%
in resources and self-sufficient.

00:08:34.930 --> 00:08:36.380 line:80%
I heard from my grandfather

00:08:36.380 --> 00:08:39.170 line:80%
that before the former chief went mad,

00:08:39.170 --> 00:08:41.140 line:80%
Li Sect lived very well.

00:08:41.140 --> 00:08:43.170 line:80%
There were markets, shops,

00:08:43.170 --> 00:08:44.530 line:80%
workshops, and eateries.

00:08:44.530 --> 00:08:46.380 line:80%
Life was peaceful and harmonious.

00:08:47.100 --> 00:08:49.410 line:80%
But it declined later.

00:08:49.410 --> 00:08:51.330 line:80%
Especially after Nie Zhe took office,

00:08:51.330 --> 00:08:53.450 line:80%
people suffered,
and resentment filled the air.

00:08:54.668 --> 00:08:57.068 line:80%
But now, the Young Master
has taken charge of Bliss Palace.

00:08:57.079 --> 00:08:58.839 line:80%
The Li Sect will soon prosper again.

00:09:01.290 --> 00:09:03.410 line:80%
He'll surely be a good chief.

00:09:03.410 --> 00:09:04.780 line:80%
Grandfather is returning soon.

00:09:04.780 --> 00:09:06.650 line:80%
I must go back to the village
to tidy up.

00:09:07.650 --> 00:09:09.330 line:80%
He'll be back so soon?

00:09:09.330 --> 00:09:10.690 line:80%
Is it unpleasant outside?

00:09:10.690 --> 00:09:12.620 line:80%
A few days outside is fine.

00:09:12.620 --> 00:09:14.140 line:80%
Too long won't do.

00:09:14.140 --> 00:09:15.690 line:80%
People outside the mountains

00:09:15.690 --> 00:09:17.410 line:80%
don't truly accept us.

00:09:17.930 --> 00:09:19.220 line:80%
It is better to return home.

00:09:20.500 --> 00:09:21.570 line:80%
Miss Cai,

00:09:23.020 --> 00:09:24.650 line:80%
will you also return home?

00:09:28.810 --> 00:09:30.050 line:80%
It is time to go back.

00:09:30.050 --> 00:09:31.500 line:80%
Otherwise, my family will worry.

00:09:31.500 --> 00:09:32.900 line:80%
If you return, the Young Master...

00:09:34.220 --> 00:09:35.620 line:80%
Greetings, Young Master.

00:09:35.620 --> 00:09:36.980 line:80%
I'll take my leave first.

00:09:40.500 --> 00:09:41.340 line:80%
You're here.

00:09:49.590 --> 00:09:51.250 line:80%
Do you want to go
to the Hanhai Mountains?

00:10:05.410 --> 00:10:07.930 line:80%
The Hanhai Mountains are so beautiful.

00:10:07.930 --> 00:10:08.810 line:80%
Yet this was the place

00:10:09.410 --> 00:10:11.530 line:80%
my father most wished to leave.

00:10:12.330 --> 00:10:13.410 line:80%
Why?

00:10:13.410 --> 00:10:15.050 line:80%
My father once said,

00:10:15.050 --> 00:10:17.450 line:80%
"The Mu clan has governed Li Sect
for 200 years."

00:10:17.450 --> 00:10:19.450 line:80%
"Every child born into the Mu clan"

00:10:19.450 --> 00:10:20.892 line:80%
"must study diligently without rest,"

00:10:20.903 --> 00:10:22.100 line:80%
"resist the Six Sects,"

00:10:23.140 --> 00:10:24.930 line:80%
"and control the unruly subordinates."

00:10:24.930 --> 00:10:26.860 line:80%
"Their entire lives are trapped here."

00:10:27.740 --> 00:10:28.580 line:80%
"It is enough."

00:10:28.930 --> 00:10:30.450 line:80%
Then why did he not leave?

00:10:30.810 --> 00:10:32.620 line:80%
Because Elder Qiu begged him bitterly.

00:10:33.220 --> 00:10:34.140 line:80%
Elder Qiu said

00:10:36.220 --> 00:10:37.620 line:80%
that if my father left,

00:10:38.740 --> 00:10:41.290 line:80%
Nie Hengcheng would act
without restraint.

00:10:41.290 --> 00:10:43.050 line:80%
Those loyal to the Mu clan

00:10:43.860 --> 00:10:45.290 line:80%
would be slaughtered.

00:10:46.450 --> 00:10:47.290 line:80%
He could not bear it,

00:10:47.780 --> 00:10:48.900 line:80%
so he stayed.

00:10:49.570 --> 00:10:51.380 line:80%
Later, he met Sun Ruoshui

00:10:52.330 --> 00:10:53.810 line:80%
and had me.

00:10:53.810 --> 00:10:55.530 line:80%
In my childhood, I suffered greatly,

00:10:55.530 --> 00:10:57.290 line:80%
barely clinging to life.

00:10:57.290 --> 00:10:58.930 line:80%
So, he stayed again.

00:10:59.980 --> 00:11:01.290 line:80%
Until two years ago,

00:11:03.410 --> 00:11:05.100 line:80%
he was poisoned by Sun Ruoshui.

00:11:05.100 --> 00:11:06.290 line:80%
Not long after,

00:11:07.740 --> 00:11:08.980 line:80%
he passed away.

00:11:09.410 --> 00:11:12.020 line:80%
So, he never managed to leave.

00:11:13.930 --> 00:11:15.020 line:80%
Mu Qingyan!

00:11:36.099 --> 00:11:37.985 line:80%
The poison has spread
to your limbs and organs.

00:11:38.410 --> 00:11:39.330 line:80%
It can't be suppressed.

00:11:40.500 --> 00:11:42.220 line:80%
Why has it suddenly worsened like this?

00:11:42.740 --> 00:11:44.450 line:80%
Suzi Fragrance has no cure.

00:11:45.900 --> 00:11:46.810 line:80%
Perhaps

00:11:48.810 --> 00:11:50.020 line:80%
the time has come.

00:11:53.620 --> 00:11:54.810 line:80%
I'll find someone to save you.

00:12:00.140 --> 00:12:02.020 line:80%
Even Uncle Lei is helpless.

00:12:04.100 --> 00:12:05.140 line:80%
In this vast world,

00:12:06.140 --> 00:12:07.330 line:80%
who else can you find?

00:12:15.380 --> 00:12:16.220 line:80%
Zhao,

00:12:18.140 --> 00:12:20.100 line:80%
I still have one unfulfilled wish.

00:12:21.620 --> 00:12:23.020 line:80%
Are you willing to help me?

00:12:23.450 --> 00:12:24.330 line:80%
What is it?

00:12:27.740 --> 00:12:29.740 line:80%
In these final days,

00:12:32.220 --> 00:12:34.450 line:80%
I hope you can stay by my side.

00:12:48.290 --> 00:12:49.130 line:80%
After all,

00:12:50.500 --> 00:12:52.020 line:80%
in my current state,

00:12:53.530 --> 00:12:55.140 line:80%
I won't delay you for long.

00:12:57.780 --> 00:12:58.620 line:80%
All right.

00:13:00.100 --> 00:13:01.020 line:80%
I'll stay with you.

00:13:21.740 --> 00:13:24.300 line:80%
(Carefree)

00:14:17.900 --> 00:14:18.740 line:80%
Young Master,

00:14:19.570 --> 00:14:20.410 line:80%
your health...

00:14:20.930 --> 00:14:21.930 line:80%
Say no more.

00:14:59.650 --> 00:15:00.650 line:80%
Yuzhi.

00:15:04.380 --> 00:15:05.220 line:80%
Zhao,

00:15:06.410 --> 00:15:07.860 line:80%
when do you plan to return?

00:15:11.780 --> 00:15:13.220 line:80%
In a few more days.

00:15:13.220 --> 00:15:15.260 line:80%
I've received a pigeon message
from Guangtian Gate.

00:15:15.570 --> 00:15:17.740 line:80%
Master and the others
are already outside.

00:15:18.220 --> 00:15:19.290 line:80%
If we don't return soon,

00:15:19.290 --> 00:15:20.500 line:80%
they might force their way in.

00:15:20.930 --> 00:15:22.020 line:80%
Zhao, have you considered

00:15:23.290 --> 00:15:24.650 line:80%
how this will end?

00:15:25.290 --> 00:15:27.100 line:80%
You may leave on your own.

00:15:31.220 --> 00:15:32.410 line:80%
Why did you come out?

00:15:32.410 --> 00:15:33.290 line:80%
It's windy outside.

00:15:33.290 --> 00:15:34.570 line:80%
Hurry back and lie down.

00:15:35.380 --> 00:15:36.220 line:80%
I'm fine.

00:15:38.980 --> 00:15:39.820 line:80%
Yuzhi,

00:15:41.500 --> 00:15:42.690 line:80%
just give me a few more days.

00:15:47.220 --> 00:15:48.140 line:80%
Go back now.

00:16:01.780 --> 00:16:02.740 line:80%
Thank you, Uncle Cheng.

00:16:04.220 --> 00:16:05.980 line:80%
You even prepared Smiley for me.

00:16:07.170 --> 00:16:08.100 line:80%
Open your mouth.

00:16:08.100 --> 00:16:08.940 line:80%
Young Master.

00:16:15.450 --> 00:16:16.290 line:80%
You...

00:16:19.570 --> 00:16:20.410 line:80%
Young Master,

00:16:20.900 --> 00:16:22.980 line:80%
are you going to repeat
the Mu clan's past mistakes?

00:16:22.980 --> 00:16:24.820 line:80%
It seems Elder Yan has
something to say to me.

00:16:25.500 --> 00:16:26.340 line:80%
Zhao,

00:16:26.780 --> 00:16:28.020 line:80%
wait outside for me.

00:16:36.690 --> 00:16:37.650 line:80%
Young Master,

00:16:37.930 --> 00:16:39.380 line:80%
the marriages of your family

00:16:39.690 --> 00:16:41.290 line:80%
have never

00:16:41.290 --> 00:16:42.930 line:80%
ended well.

00:16:43.330 --> 00:16:45.740 line:80%
The Young Lord suffered deeply.

00:16:45.740 --> 00:16:47.900 line:80%
Why must you repeat the same mistake?

00:16:47.900 --> 00:16:49.860 line:80%
You've only been released
for a few days.

00:16:51.170 --> 00:16:53.530 line:80%
Do you wish to be locked back
in the Jiuzhou Archive?

00:16:54.290 --> 00:16:55.810 line:80%
You can even throw me into the dungeon.

00:16:56.570 --> 00:16:58.220 line:80%
Today, I must speak my mind.

00:16:58.530 --> 00:17:00.930 line:80%
The Li Sect now stands amid ruins.

00:17:01.570 --> 00:17:04.370 line:80%
This is your opportunity
to accomplish something.

00:17:04.370 --> 00:17:05.210 line:80%
And now?

00:17:05.220 --> 00:17:06.810 line:80%
For Miss Cai,

00:17:06.810 --> 00:17:08.940 line:80%
you linger
in the Carefree Chamber all day,

00:17:08.940 --> 00:17:10.330 line:80%
lost in warmth and comfort,

00:17:10.330 --> 00:17:11.740 line:80%
neglecting progress.

00:17:11.740 --> 00:17:13.180 line:80%
Do you wish to doom Li Sect?

00:17:13.570 --> 00:17:14.810 line:80%
My father's dying wish

00:17:15.370 --> 00:17:16.610 line:80%
was to dissolve Li Sect

00:17:17.180 --> 00:17:18.500 line:80%
and leave the Hanhai Mountains.

00:17:18.500 --> 00:17:19.340 line:80%
Perhaps

00:17:20.090 --> 00:17:21.383 line:80%
I should issue the order at once

00:17:21.780 --> 00:17:23.570 line:80%
and let the members depart freely.

00:17:24.020 --> 00:17:25.330 line:80%
Would that not satisfy all?

00:17:26.700 --> 00:17:27.660 line:80%
Young Master,

00:17:31.850 --> 00:17:33.220 line:80%
forgive my bluntness.

00:17:34.460 --> 00:17:35.890 line:80%
The one who killed the Young Lord

00:17:35.890 --> 00:17:36.980 line:80%
was not Nie Zhe,

00:17:36.980 --> 00:17:38.420 line:80%
nor Sun Ruoshui,

00:17:38.420 --> 00:17:40.330 line:80%
but his merciful heart.

00:17:40.330 --> 00:17:41.850 line:80%
His mercy

00:17:41.850 --> 00:17:42.810 line:80%
could not even

00:17:43.460 --> 00:17:44.610 line:80%
protect himself.

00:17:45.050 --> 00:17:45.890 line:80%
Young Master,

00:17:46.220 --> 00:17:47.940 line:80%
don't repeat the same mistake.

00:17:47.940 --> 00:17:48.850 line:80%
Elder Yan,

00:17:50.610 --> 00:17:51.610 line:80%
what a man my father was

00:17:52.500 --> 00:17:54.220 line:80%
isn't for you to judge.

00:17:56.330 --> 00:17:57.740 line:80%
I don't care who he was.

00:17:58.020 --> 00:17:59.220 line:80%
He was a Mu.

00:17:59.890 --> 00:18:01.610 line:80%
A Mu

00:18:01.610 --> 00:18:03.370 line:80%
can't think only of themselves.

00:18:03.810 --> 00:18:05.610 line:80%
For all the sect members,

00:18:05.610 --> 00:18:07.570 line:80%
this is their home.

00:18:07.570 --> 00:18:09.020 line:80%
If Li Sect prospers,

00:18:09.020 --> 00:18:10.460 line:80%
we live and work in peace.

00:18:10.890 --> 00:18:12.850 line:80%
If Li Sect is gone,

00:18:12.850 --> 00:18:13.890 line:80%
we lose our home

00:18:13.890 --> 00:18:15.090 line:80%
and suffer humiliation.

00:18:17.570 --> 00:18:18.410 line:80%
Young Master,

00:18:18.570 --> 00:18:20.740 line:80%
if you insist on going your own way,

00:18:20.740 --> 00:18:22.370 line:80%
I'll release Nie Zhe at once

00:18:22.370 --> 00:18:23.530 line:80%
and restore him as the Chief.

00:18:23.530 --> 00:18:25.090 line:80%
Even if he acts tyrannically again,

00:18:25.090 --> 00:18:27.290 line:80%
at least he can protect

00:18:27.290 --> 00:18:29.290 line:80%
this ancestral foundation
for the sec members.

00:18:34.420 --> 00:18:35.260 line:80%
It seems you

00:18:36.899 --> 00:18:38.405 line:80%
truly have my best interests at heart.

00:18:40.050 --> 00:18:40.890 line:80%
Young Master,

00:18:41.370 --> 00:18:43.020 line:80%
please correct your actions now.

00:18:43.460 --> 00:18:44.570 line:80%
But if I did not do this,

00:18:46.180 --> 00:18:48.660 line:80%
how could I lure out Nie Zhe's remnants

00:18:49.740 --> 00:18:51.050 line:80%
and wipe them out in one sweep?

00:19:02.180 --> 00:19:04.046 line:80%
Once most of Nie Zhe's followers
are captured,

00:19:04.780 --> 00:19:06.530 line:80%
Mr. Mu should recover, right?

00:19:07.660 --> 00:19:09.073 line:80%
His chronic illness is hard to cure.

00:19:09.293 --> 00:19:10.290 line:80%
He won't recover so soon.

00:19:10.500 --> 00:19:11.810 line:80%
If it were truly that serious,

00:19:12.500 --> 00:19:14.780 line:80%
would you and You
hunt down rebels everywhere?

00:19:17.510 --> 00:19:18.878 line:80%
It's just a plan to lure the enemy

00:19:18.889 --> 00:19:19.700 line:80%
and stall for time,

00:19:19.700 --> 00:19:21.330 line:80%
killing two birds with one stone.

00:19:23.500 --> 00:19:24.340 line:80%
Don't worry.

00:19:25.130 --> 00:19:26.980 line:80%
This is your internal matter.

00:19:26.980 --> 00:19:27.820 line:80%
I won't interfere.

00:19:29.610 --> 00:19:30.649 line:80%
As for Miss Cai...

00:19:30.660 --> 00:19:32.109 line:80%
She's involved too deeply to see it.

00:19:32.610 --> 00:19:34.090 line:80%
No matter what others say,

00:19:34.090 --> 00:19:35.940 line:80%
she should see through the maze herself.

00:19:36.740 --> 00:19:37.890 line:80%
Zhao is intelligent.

00:19:37.890 --> 00:19:39.090 line:80%
She'll see it on her own.

00:19:39.660 --> 00:19:41.570 line:80%
Before that, I won't say another word.

00:19:42.420 --> 00:19:43.260 line:80%
What a pity

00:19:43.890 --> 00:19:45.610 line:80%
that you're from the Six Sects.

00:19:45.890 --> 00:19:46.980 line:80%
In the future, we may gain

00:19:47.660 --> 00:19:49.020 line:80%
another formidable enemy.

00:20:13.036 --> 00:20:14.810 line:80%
She can't even swallow
her medicine anymore.

00:20:14.810 --> 00:20:15.650 line:80%
Mother,

00:20:16.530 --> 00:20:18.130 line:80%
is Aunt going to die?

00:20:31.680 --> 00:20:32.530 line:80%
Aunt,

00:20:32.530 --> 00:20:33.370 line:80%
take the medicine.

00:20:40.050 --> 00:20:40.890 line:80%
Aunt!

00:20:51.050 --> 00:20:51.890 line:80%
Qi,

00:20:53.180 --> 00:20:54.020 line:80%
Pingshu

00:20:55.290 --> 00:20:56.660 line:80%
is gone.

00:20:58.530 --> 00:20:59.570 line:80%
Qi,

00:20:59.940 --> 00:21:00.780 line:80%
don't be like this.

00:21:01.180 --> 00:21:02.570 line:80%
Qi, don't be like this.

00:21:02.570 --> 00:21:03.410 line:80%
Qi...

00:21:08.530 --> 00:21:09.370 line:80%
Qi!

00:21:09.940 --> 00:21:10.850 line:80%
Pingshu.

00:21:13.330 --> 00:21:14.220 line:80%
Pingshu!

00:21:14.220 --> 00:21:16.220 line:80%
She's gone. Qi, don't be like this.

00:21:16.220 --> 00:21:18.050 line:80%
- Qi!
- Pingshu!

00:21:18.050 --> 00:21:19.700 line:80%
Don't be like this, Qi!

00:21:19.700 --> 00:21:20.610 line:80%
Pingshu!

00:21:24.890 --> 00:21:26.570 line:80%
Why must they die?

00:21:31.330 --> 00:21:33.290 line:80%
Why can't I do anything?

00:22:06.020 --> 00:22:06.860 line:80%
Mu Qingyan.

00:22:19.130 --> 00:22:19.970 line:80%
Zhao,

00:22:20.850 --> 00:22:21.690 line:80%
you are here.

00:22:22.420 --> 00:22:23.610 line:80%
Yan Xu is too rigid.

00:22:24.020 --> 00:22:25.290 line:80%
I've driven him away.

00:22:26.050 --> 00:22:27.700 line:80%
He won't disturb us again.

00:22:31.020 --> 00:22:31.860 line:80%
Zhao,

00:22:33.290 --> 00:22:34.130 line:80%
what is wrong?

00:22:34.940 --> 00:22:36.420 line:80%
I've left the sect without permission

00:22:36.740 --> 00:22:38.180 line:80%
for over two months.

00:22:38.980 --> 00:22:40.530 line:80%
It's time for me to return.

00:22:42.330 --> 00:22:43.330 line:80%
Today,

00:22:43.660 --> 00:22:44.890 line:80%
I came to say goodbye.

00:22:45.610 --> 00:22:46.530 line:80%
What did you say?

00:22:47.460 --> 00:22:48.850 line:80%
I said I'm leaving.

00:22:48.850 --> 00:22:50.130 line:80%
I'm returning to Qingque Sect.

00:22:50.610 --> 00:22:51.890 line:80%
This is the demonic sect.

00:22:51.890 --> 00:22:53.780 line:80%
I'm a disciple of the Six Sects.

00:22:53.780 --> 00:22:55.330 line:80%
You've become the Chief.

00:22:56.050 --> 00:22:57.530 line:80%
I can't stay any longer.

00:22:58.090 --> 00:22:59.220 line:80%
But you promised me

00:23:01.180 --> 00:23:02.500 line:80%
to stay with me.

00:23:04.980 --> 00:23:06.020 line:80%
For how long?

00:23:09.700 --> 00:23:10.540 line:80%
One year?

00:23:13.660 --> 00:23:14.610 line:80%
Five years?

00:23:17.780 --> 00:23:19.020 line:80%
Or ten years?

00:23:22.610 --> 00:23:23.660 line:80%
You need not worry.

00:23:24.890 --> 00:23:26.330 line:80%
This poison won't take that long.

00:23:31.370 --> 00:23:32.940 line:80%
That may not be so.

00:23:34.460 --> 00:23:36.530 line:80%
You're blessed with talent.

00:23:36.530 --> 00:23:37.890 line:80%
Would mere Suzi Fragrance

00:23:37.890 --> 00:23:39.570 line:80%
truly defeat you?

00:23:39.570 --> 00:23:40.740 line:80%
What are you talking about?

00:23:49.780 --> 00:23:51.460 line:80%
What clever tactics.

00:23:52.020 --> 00:23:54.460 line:80%
Using the more potent Xungu Grass

00:23:54.460 --> 00:23:56.020 line:80%
to trigger a new poison.

00:23:56.020 --> 00:23:58.370 line:80%
It suppresses
the outbreak of Suzi Fragrance

00:23:58.370 --> 00:23:59.610 line:80%
and lets you stage a fine act

00:23:59.610 --> 00:24:00.940 line:80%
of being near death before me.

00:24:01.660 --> 00:24:03.020 line:80%
How ruthless.

00:24:04.050 --> 00:24:04.890 line:80%
Zhao,

00:24:06.290 --> 00:24:07.130 line:80%
I...

00:24:09.500 --> 00:24:10.340 line:80%
No.

00:24:12.570 --> 00:24:14.090 line:80%
You didn't act for me.

00:24:14.780 --> 00:24:17.700 line:80%
You acted for the whole world.

00:24:18.420 --> 00:24:19.570 line:80%
I was wondering

00:24:20.530 --> 00:24:21.980 line:80%
why, with your poison flaring,

00:24:22.700 --> 00:24:24.420 line:80%
Shangguan Haonan and You Guanyue

00:24:24.420 --> 00:24:26.090 line:80%
were nowhere to be seen.

00:24:26.090 --> 00:24:27.290 line:80%
Now, I understand.

00:24:28.090 --> 00:24:30.130 line:80%
They are busy capturing
Nie Zhe's followers.

00:24:31.020 --> 00:24:32.500 line:80%
With you poisoned,

00:24:32.940 --> 00:24:34.370 line:80%
unable to attend to greater matters,

00:24:35.330 --> 00:24:36.530 line:80%
those remnants

00:24:36.530 --> 00:24:38.290 line:80%
would surely reveal themselves.

00:24:38.290 --> 00:24:40.220 line:80%
Then you cleanse them in blood.

00:24:40.220 --> 00:24:41.330 line:80%
Two birds with one arrow.

00:24:41.330 --> 00:24:42.660 line:80%
Truly an excellent scheme.

00:24:42.660 --> 00:24:44.050 line:80%
Zhao...

00:24:46.420 --> 00:24:47.260 line:80%
Zhao!

00:24:49.130 --> 00:24:50.700 line:80%
I just wanted you to stay.

00:24:53.290 --> 00:24:54.370 line:80%
This is Li Sect.

00:24:54.370 --> 00:24:55.370 line:80%
(Carefree)

00:24:55.370 --> 00:24:56.610 line:80%
Do you think you can leave

00:24:57.660 --> 00:24:59.130 line:80%
without my permission?

00:25:01.020 --> 00:25:01.940 line:80%
Mu Qingyan,

00:25:03.370 --> 00:25:04.460 line:80%
why must it be like this?

00:25:05.090 --> 00:25:06.940 line:80%
We had this journey

00:25:06.940 --> 00:25:08.090 line:80%
only by fate.

00:25:09.130 --> 00:25:10.740 line:80%
Now that fate has ended,

00:25:11.700 --> 00:25:13.020 line:80%
it's time to part peacefully.

00:25:13.020 --> 00:25:14.130 line:80%
That's nonsense.

00:25:15.290 --> 00:25:17.020 line:80%
You're just timid,

00:25:17.020 --> 00:25:18.130 line:80%
afraid of being blamed.

00:25:20.433 --> 00:25:22.739 line:80%
Have you forgotten what we saw
in the underground palace?

00:25:23.420 --> 00:25:25.940 line:80%
Mu Donglie and Luo Shiyun
could overcome countless hardships.

00:25:25.940 --> 00:25:26.850 line:80%
So can we.

00:25:27.370 --> 00:25:29.020 line:80%
Mu Qingyan, wake up.

00:25:29.020 --> 00:25:30.330 line:80%
With Mu Donglie's power,

00:25:30.330 --> 00:25:31.570 line:80%
even he could not openly

00:25:31.570 --> 00:25:33.180 line:80%
marry Luo Shiyun.

00:25:33.180 --> 00:25:34.706 line:80%
He either hid in an underground palace

00:25:34.717 --> 00:25:35.500 line:80%
or fled far away.

00:25:36.130 --> 00:25:37.530 line:80%
Let alone you and me.

00:25:37.980 --> 00:25:39.460 line:80%
What could we possibly do?

00:25:40.530 --> 00:25:42.220 line:80%
The demonic sect

00:25:42.220 --> 00:25:43.070 line:80%
and the Six Sects

00:25:43.080 --> 00:25:44.330 line:80%
are irreconcilable enemies.

00:25:44.330 --> 00:25:46.020 line:80%
I cannot abandon my family

00:25:46.020 --> 00:25:47.420 line:80%
and duties for you.

00:25:47.420 --> 00:25:48.940 line:80%
I'd never do that for anyone!

00:25:49.370 --> 00:25:50.210 line:80%
You can't leave!

00:25:54.610 --> 00:25:56.460 line:80%
If you insist on keeping me...

00:25:57.980 --> 00:26:00.660 line:80%
This blade has taken many lives.

00:26:01.570 --> 00:26:04.090 line:80%
I won't disgrace my aunt's name.

00:26:06.850 --> 00:26:08.050 line:80%
You want to kill me?

00:26:26.700 --> 00:26:27.700 line:80%
Let me go.

00:26:36.660 --> 00:26:38.016 line:80%
Young Master, bad news!

00:26:38.027 --> 00:26:39.260 line:80%
(Carefree)
Nie Zhe was rescued.

00:26:43.610 --> 00:26:44.530 line:80%
Miss Cai,

00:26:44.530 --> 00:26:45.980 line:80%
that isn't how to hold a blade.

00:26:45.980 --> 00:26:46.940 line:80%
It's so frightening.

00:26:49.130 --> 00:26:49.970 line:80%
Speak.

00:26:52.810 --> 00:26:53.650 line:80%
Young Master,

00:26:53.940 --> 00:26:55.740 line:80%
a man in black
just broke into the dungeon,

00:26:55.740 --> 00:26:57.050 line:80%
injured Shisan, rescued Nie Zhe,

00:26:57.050 --> 00:26:57.890 line:80%
and...

00:26:59.180 --> 00:27:00.530 line:80%
killed Lady Sun.

00:27:22.500 --> 00:27:23.340 line:80%
You may go.

00:27:24.090 --> 00:27:24.930 line:80%
Catch them first.

00:27:25.180 --> 00:27:27.220 line:80%
No need for you
to trouble yourself with that.

00:27:27.220 --> 00:27:29.020 line:80%
Were you not ready to leave just now?

00:27:29.570 --> 00:27:31.330 line:80%
The one who killed Uncle Chang

00:27:32.780 --> 00:27:34.020 line:80%
must be dealt with.

00:27:34.020 --> 00:27:35.890 line:80%
You can stay for one day.

00:27:36.740 --> 00:27:38.530 line:80%
But what about a month? A year?

00:27:38.530 --> 00:27:39.740 line:80%
You come

00:27:39.740 --> 00:27:40.810 line:80%
and go as you please.

00:27:42.610 --> 00:27:43.890 line:80%
What do you take Li Sect for?

00:27:44.850 --> 00:27:46.220 line:80%
If you wish to stay,

00:27:47.700 --> 00:27:49.370 line:80%
you may never leave.

00:27:50.330 --> 00:27:51.449 line:80%
Have you thought it through?

00:28:09.460 --> 00:28:10.300 line:80%
Miss Cai...

00:29:31.849 --> 00:29:33.406 line:80%
The strike pierced the Baihui acupoint.

00:29:33.417 --> 00:29:34.267 line:80%
Death was instant.

00:29:34.890 --> 00:29:36.076 line:80%
There should've been no pain.

00:29:36.660 --> 00:29:38.180 line:80%
We've searched everywhere.

00:29:38.363 --> 00:29:40.330 line:80%
There is no trace of Nie Zhe
or the man in black.

00:29:40.330 --> 00:29:41.170 line:80%
Could it be

00:29:41.879 --> 00:29:43.130 line:80%
that there is a secret passage?

00:29:43.130 --> 00:29:44.930 line:80%
The Nie clan controlled
the sect for decades.

00:29:45.530 --> 00:29:46.910 line:80%
A cunning rabbit has three burrows.

00:29:47.660 --> 00:29:49.306 line:80%
A secret passage
would not be surprising.

00:29:49.740 --> 00:29:50.980 line:80%
But this man in black

00:29:51.700 --> 00:29:53.980 line:80%
knows the Nie clan's secrets so well.

00:29:58.113 --> 00:30:00.066 line:80%
Bury her according to the rites
of a chief's wife

00:30:01.180 --> 00:30:02.290 line:80%
with full honors.

00:30:02.610 --> 00:30:03.530 line:80%
Young Master...

00:30:03.530 --> 00:30:04.370 line:80%
All of you, leave.

00:30:09.570 --> 00:30:10.410 line:80%
Yes.

00:30:17.680 --> 00:30:19.200 line:80%
The Young Master seems in low spirits.

00:30:21.460 --> 00:30:22.460 line:80%
If only Miss Cai

00:30:22.810 --> 00:30:23.650 line:80%
were here.

00:31:21.220 --> 00:31:22.060 line:80%
Zhao!

00:31:23.020 --> 00:31:23.860 line:80%
Master.

00:31:26.290 --> 00:31:28.050 line:80%
We truly share a bond.

00:31:28.398 --> 00:31:29.768 line:80%
I've been thinking of you for days.

00:31:29.779 --> 00:31:30.779 line:80%
And you came to fetch me.

00:31:31.180 --> 00:31:32.020 line:80%
Come on.

00:31:32.610 --> 00:31:33.450 line:80%
Were you injured?

00:31:34.500 --> 00:31:35.340 line:80%
Good to hear.

00:31:42.850 --> 00:31:43.810 line:80%
The priority now

00:31:43.810 --> 00:31:45.130 line:80%
is to find the man in black,

00:31:45.130 --> 00:31:46.050 line:80%
avenge Uncle Chang,

00:31:46.980 --> 00:31:48.660 line:80%
and prevent further disaster.

00:31:49.660 --> 00:31:50.500 line:80%
Zhao,

00:31:51.850 --> 00:31:54.500 line:80%
do you truly believe
what Mu Qingyan says?

00:31:54.500 --> 00:31:56.500 line:80%
If he could impersonate Chang Ning,

00:31:56.500 --> 00:31:58.810 line:80%
why could he not fabricate
a man in black

00:31:58.810 --> 00:31:59.940 line:80%
and stage a play for you?

00:32:00.740 --> 00:32:01.640 line:80%
Master,

00:32:01.640 --> 00:32:03.290 line:80%
I've fought that man in black.

00:32:03.290 --> 00:32:04.370 line:80%
He is indeed unfathomable.

00:32:04.660 --> 00:32:06.020 line:80%
By your account,

00:32:06.020 --> 00:32:07.940 line:80%
among the Seven Star Elders,

00:32:07.940 --> 00:32:09.290 line:80%
two still remain.

00:32:09.740 --> 00:32:10.650 line:80%
It's possible

00:32:10.650 --> 00:32:12.660 line:80%
that this man in black
is a hidden third elder.

00:32:14.370 --> 00:32:15.670 line:80%
They're inexperienced and unaware

00:32:16.020 --> 00:32:17.396 line:80%
of how cunning the demonic sect is.

00:32:17.610 --> 00:32:18.443 line:80%
Mu Qingyan,

00:32:18.454 --> 00:32:20.050 line:80%
as the Young Master
of the demonic sect,

00:32:20.050 --> 00:32:22.780 line:80%
disguised himself as Chang Ning
in Qingque Sect for months.

00:32:22.780 --> 00:32:24.940 line:80%
Even I was deceived by him.

00:32:24.940 --> 00:32:28.050 line:80%
One who possesses such scheming
is no ordinary person.

00:32:28.050 --> 00:32:30.020 line:80%
Once a fraud, always a fraud.

00:32:30.020 --> 00:32:32.136 line:80%
Yet you, for such a deceitful man,

00:32:32.147 --> 00:32:33.876 line:80%
involved yourselves
in the internal strife.

00:32:33.887 --> 00:32:35.257 line:80%
What do you take

00:32:35.360 --> 00:32:36.530 line:80%
Qingque Sect,

00:32:37.220 --> 00:32:39.130 line:80%
your own lives,

00:32:39.130 --> 00:32:41.090 line:80%
and your loved ones for?

00:32:41.090 --> 00:32:41.930 line:80%
Yunke.

00:32:43.740 --> 00:32:44.580 line:80%
Yuzhi,

00:32:44.850 --> 00:32:45.740 line:80%
Zhao,

00:32:45.740 --> 00:32:47.740 line:80%
you two snuck away this time.

00:32:47.740 --> 00:32:49.949 line:80%
Your master was worried sick.

00:32:49.960 --> 00:32:50.940 line:80%
If I hadn't stopped him,

00:32:50.951 --> 00:32:52.460 line:80%
he'd have ridden into the Youming Path

00:32:52.460 --> 00:32:53.300 line:80%
to rescue you.

00:32:56.130 --> 00:32:57.940 line:80%
We even had to find ways

00:32:57.940 --> 00:32:59.460 line:80%
to protect your reputations.

00:32:59.460 --> 00:33:00.673 line:80%
There must not be a next time.

00:33:01.180 --> 00:33:02.660 line:80%
It was my fault.

00:33:04.850 --> 00:33:06.740 line:80%
I won't make you worry again.

00:33:15.940 --> 00:33:17.220 line:80%
Milady,

00:33:17.220 --> 00:33:18.740 line:80%
you are finally back.

00:33:18.740 --> 00:33:20.090 line:80%
Was the trip smooth?

00:33:20.090 --> 00:33:21.420 line:80%
Did anything interesting happen?

00:33:22.810 --> 00:33:23.650 line:80%
Nothing.

00:33:26.420 --> 00:33:28.050 line:80%
Are you hungry?

00:33:28.050 --> 00:33:29.220 line:80%
Would you like some wonton?

00:33:29.220 --> 00:33:30.740 line:80%
When I heard you were returning,

00:33:30.740 --> 00:33:31.940 line:80%
I learned how to make them.

00:33:31.940 --> 00:33:33.626 line:80%
I even prepared
the front of the pork leg.

00:33:35.890 --> 00:33:36.740 line:80%
The wonton is here.

00:34:18.507 --> 00:34:20.587 line:80%
Mu Qingyan, as the Young Master
of the demonic sect,

00:34:20.850 --> 00:34:22.260 line:80%
disguised himself as Chang Ning

00:34:22.270 --> 00:34:24.220 line:80%
in Qingque Sect for months.

00:34:24.220 --> 00:34:25.450 line:80%
Once a fraud,

00:34:25.450 --> 00:34:26.410 line:80%
always a fraud.

00:34:26.930 --> 00:34:29.540 line:80%
Yet you, for such a deceitful man,

00:34:29.540 --> 00:34:31.280 line:80%
involved yourselves
in the internal strife.

00:34:31.930 --> 00:34:32.930 line:80%
What do you take

00:34:33.780 --> 00:34:34.810 line:80%
Qingque Sect,

00:34:35.410 --> 00:34:36.780 line:80%
your own lives,

00:34:37.540 --> 00:34:39.010 line:80%
and your loved ones for?

00:35:01.450 --> 00:35:02.290 line:80%
Milady.

00:35:04.740 --> 00:35:05.580 line:80%
Milady?

00:35:19.580 --> 00:35:21.060 line:80%
I'll never eat wonton again.

00:35:21.740 --> 00:35:22.970 line:80%
Don't mention wonton again.

